Armstrong Shaw - Product











Armstrong Shaw has a disciplined, absolute value approach to the equity market.  We believe that investing in high quality businesses run by proven management teams at attractive prices will provide superior returns to our clients over time.  We seek to provide attractive long term returns by investing in a concentrated portfolio assembled through bottom up, fundamentally driven stock selection.  We invest in securities when cash flow or asset value analysis determines they are selling at a substantial discount to intrinsic value.  We focus on companies that generate predictable and sustainable free cash flows.  High cash flow generation allows for increased research and development, the ability to capitalize quickly on opportunities, make acquisitions to further grow the business, or return value to shareholders.  We also compare the company's valutation to its peers, the broader market, and any transactions that may have taken place in its industry.  We interview the management team to get a better sense of the strategic and financial plans for the company.  Ultimately, our goal is to purchase these stocks at prices equal to or less than 70% of our estimate of intrinsic value.HomeProductInvestment TeamContactTerms of UseCompany Specific Analysis - What We Look ForArmstrong Shaw Associates Inc., 237 Elm Street, New Canaan, CT 06840ph: 203.972.9600   fx: 203.972.9635   marketing@armstrongshaw.com   www.armstrongshaw.comYour use of this site signifies that you accept our Terms Of Use.Privacy PolicyOur Product


















