ARMSTRONG SHAW ASSOCIATES INC. : Top Money Managers  










Armstrong Shaw











Armstrong Shaw Associates Inc., an SEC registered investment advisor located in New Canaan, Connecticut, has been providing large cap equity management to institutional and individual clients since its founding in 1984.  We are privately owned with a seasoned investment team that averages 24 years of experience.  Our investment philosophy is rooted in a disciplined, absolute value approach to the equity market.  We seek to provide strong absolute returns by investing in a concentrated portfolio assembled through bottom up, fundamentally driven stock selection.HomeProductInvestment TeamContactTerms of UseArmstrong Shaw Associates Inc., 237 Elm Street, New Canaan, CT 06840ph: 203.972.9600   fx: 203.972.9635   marketing@armstrongshaw.com   www.armstrongshaw.comYour use of this site signifies that you accept our Terms Of Use.Privacy Policy

•Employee owned with continuity of management since 1984•Single product; sole focus•Concentrated portfolio where every name counts•Fundamental stock pickers with a disciplined, absolute value approach•Long term value added attributable to stock selection•Strong emphasis on client serviceKey Characteristics That Distinguish Armstrong Shaw  The Firm









 



